    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Emergency measures taken by archaeologists to survey, excavate, and salvage at sites imminently threatened by land modification projects such as roads, buildings, and reservoir construction.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051089/AATA database (2002-) </Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000114707/Oxford English Dictionary Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000093511/Library of Congress Authorities online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Noodmaatregelen die door archeologen worden genomen om onderzoek, opgravingen en reddingsoperaties uit te voeren op sites die worden bedreigd door projecten waarbij het land wordt aangetast, bijvoorbeeld de bouw van wegen, gebouwen of reservoirs.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000109894/UvA Talen</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Notfallmaßnahmen von Archäologen zur Auffindung, Ausgrabung und Rettung archäologischer Stätten, die unmittelbar von Baumaßnahmen wie Straßen- oder Hausbau oder der Anlage von Stauseen bedroht sind.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000232/IfM-SMB-PK</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
